{"tid":133631,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實將興趣變為工作係咪一件好事","createTime":"2017-02-24T18:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T05:25:46.000Z","uid":34785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b919e464d04e8d476665a5076d5eced38a466324","tid":133631,"uid":34785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:00:49.000Z","msg":"優點，做野個陣會特別起勁，點做都唔覺得厭，因為你真係好鐘意個樣野<br />\n<br />\n缺點，番工放工諗住同一樣野，會唔會唔健康不平衡<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲點睇"},{"pid":"1d51b17d15c3c18afaa358ce54379c116c71fc01","tid":133631,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:41:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b40a336963fcd7570b01b79bc1804c524b2f32ad","tid":133631,"uid":62045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:45:42.000Z","msg":"做得多可能會慢慢討厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6d9fea9bbc5b4f63d4f1886ea2162f728bef66","tid":133631,"uid":66679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:51:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d77cea9272bc9844662013340e8fb98828540eab","tid":133631,"uid":34785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:08:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾有興趣都好 一做職業就好快厭<br />\n日日都對住 唔想做時逼住做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係咁諗，到時可能連個興趣都失去埋，但係可以做自己鐘意的行業，又好似夢想成真咁"},{"pid":"f38e5bcea82653da52d5ee8a89119731ca0144c5","tid":133631,"uid":3325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:11:00.000Z","msg":"好撚鐘意份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2caf6b8cf5ad65429b53a7bb891c72b1e49405c5","tid":133631,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"要分得清楚收工就收工，興趣做職業同平時返工一樣會做好多唔情願嘅野"},{"pid":"4f7fe0b5e35fc82d6b4e0e6c91b8b9212fa5f7e9","tid":133631,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:08:44.000Z","msg":"會為咗市場需求而做一啲你無鍾意嘅嘢<br />\n但如果唔去試就一定會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：正職兼職都係我嘅興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0027c8de5350bed659eec1aae33ef97932bce99e","tid":133631,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:29:14.000Z","msg":"會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cbf1892d94a4701984645d2e13c6d958844c52","tid":133631,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:38:26.000Z","msg":"男優"},{"pid":"a9d7671ffcfd1d96ca9d1e0e48cda8a945be8a89","tid":133631,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"我翻一份飲食pt 學校放假翻ft時間<br />\n攰到仆街 但好鍾意d同事 翻工好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最癲個排連續廿日翻 日日十個鐘<br />\n<br />\n但反而身體仲好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a379e2a86074812fb8209475371be56f2a2304ca","tid":133631,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T05:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我翻一份飲食pt 學校放假翻ft時間<br />\n攰到仆街 但好鍾意d同事 翻工好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最癲個排連續廿日翻 日日十個鐘<br />\n<br />\n但反而身體仲好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n翻呢份前一黎m就病，差唔多每個月病一次，宜家約半年先病一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11bcd3610a19a3c37ccc20297114cd03bc17705","tid":133631,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我翻一份飲食pt 學校放假翻ft時間<br />\n攰到仆街 但好鍾意d同事 翻工好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最癲個排連續廿日翻 日日十個鐘<br />\n<br />\n但反而身體仲好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n翻呢份前一黎m就病，差唔多每個月病一次，宜家約半年先病一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返緊鍾意嘅工真係會病少啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對上一次感冒講緊係一兩年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}